---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';

import MainLayout from '../../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../../components/Header.astro';
import Sidebar from '../../../components/Sidebar.astro';

import quicksortExHomeImg from '../../../images/pvts/quicksort-example-home.png';
import listExImg from '../../../images/pvts/list-example.png';
import callsExImg from '../../../images/pvts/calls-example.png';
import envExImg from '../../../images/pvts/environment-example.png';
import fibExImg from '../../../images/pvts/fibonacci-4.png';
import competeExImg from '../../../images/pvts/pvts-compete-example-home.png';
---

<MainLayout>
  <Header promptDir="projects/pvts" />
  <div class="page-body">
    <Sidebar/>
    <main>
      <div class="content-header">
        <h1>
          <span class="section-hash">#</span>
          <span class="section-title">pvts</span>
        </h1>
        <span class="section-line" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <a href="/projects/pvts">
              <span class="link-prefix">:</span>home ↗
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/projects/pvts/download">
              <span class="link-prefix">:</span>download ↗
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/projects/pvts/language">
              <span class="link-prefix">:</span>language ↗
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <section class="hero">
        <h2>Ever wondered what the Quicksort Algorithm looks like?</h2>
        <p>
          Visualize lists, pointers and function calls in <strong>your code</strong>.
          PVTS is a visual interpreter for the Scheme functional programming language.
        </p>
        <p>It is great for teachers and students as a supporting learning tool.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <button class="btn-primary" id="btn-quicksort">
            <span class="link-prefix">:</span>click here to see the answer →
          </button>
          <div class="hero-download">
            <a class="btn-secondary" href="https://github.com/davidpilo/pvts/blob/master/dist/0.243/PVTS.jar?raw=true" target="_blank">
              <span class="link-prefix">:</span>Or download PVTS.jar now from github.com ↗
            </a> 
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="hero-note">
          PVTS is an executable JAR file and requires the Java Runtime Environment (JRE).
          <a href="http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html" target="_blank">Get it here.</a>
        </p>
      </section>

      <dialog id="modal-quicksort">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <p class="modal-title">
            This figure shows what coding and running the Quicksort algorithm for this list: <code>(5 22 13 1)</code> in PVTS:
          </p>
          <button class="modal-close" id="btn-close-modal"><span class="link-prefix">:</span>close ✕</button>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
          <Image
            src={quicksortExHomeImg}
            alt="Quicksort example"
          />
        </div>
      </dialog>

      <hr />

      <section class="features">
        <div class="feature">
          <Image src={listExImg} alt="List example" />
          <h2>Linked List Viewer</h2>
          <p>PVTS will show you all the linked lists you have in your code. It will help you understand how pointers in linked-lists work.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <Image src={callsExImg} alt="Calls example" />
          <h2>Function Call Viewer</h2>
          <p>Binary functions as Fibonacci are more easily understood visually. PVTS will draw the functions you defined and called.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <Image src={envExImg} alt="Environment example" />
          <h2>Environment Viewer</h2>
          <p>Keep track of the variables and functions you have defined in the global environment. A list of these variables and functions is easily accessible to review them.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <hr />

      <section class="example">
        <div class="example-text">
          <h2>Fibonacci Function Calls <span class="muted">example</span></h2>
          <p>
            The figure on the right is an example of running the code below in the PVTS visual
            interpreter that demonstrates how the Fibonacci Algorithm works in a functional
            programming environment.
          </p>
          <pre><code>; Lets define Fibonacci:
(define (fib n)
  (cond
    ((= n 1) 1)
    ((= n 0) 0)
    (else (+ (fib (- n 1)) (fib (- n 2))))))

; (fib 6) evaluates to
(fib 6)</code></pre>
        </div>
        <Image src={fibExImg} alt="Fibonacci function calls example" />
      </section>

      <hr />

      <section class="learn">
        <h2>Let PVTS help you learn the basics of functional programming in Scheme.</h2>
        <p>
          Although Pilo Visual Tools for Scheme is a basic interpreter
          (<a href="https://github.com/davidpilo/pvts" target="_blank">learn more about PVTS language support</a>),
          anybody that is learning the basics of recursion or wants to enhance their understanding
          of how pointers and lists work can benefit from giving this a try.
        </p>
        <Image src={competeExImg} alt="PVTS complete example" />
      </section>

      <hr />

      <footer class="page-footer">
        <a href="https://github.com/davidpilo/pvts" target="_blank">
          <span class="link-prefix">:</span>Project site on github.com ↗
        </a>
        <a href="#top">
          <span class="link-prefix">:</span>Back to top ↑
        </a>
      </footer>

    </main>
  </div>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .page-body {
    display: flex;
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 72rem;
  }

  main {
    border-left: 1px solid var(--sidebar-border);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    flex: 1;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
  }

  .content-header {
    align-items: center;
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .content-header h1 {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .content-header ul {
    align-items: center;
    display: flex;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    gap: 1rem;
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  h1 {
    align-items: center;
    display: flex;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .section-hash {
    color: var(--section-hash);
  }

  .section-title {
    color: var(--section-title);
    text-decoration: none;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .section-line {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--section-line);
    flex: 1;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0.75rem 0 0.5rem;
    color: var(--body-fg);
  }

  p {
    color: var(--p-color);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  a {
    color: var(--project-link);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  hr {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--sidebar-border);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .hero {
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.9rem;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    align-items: flex-start;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .hero-download {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .btn-primary,
  .btn-secondary {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    color: var(--project-title);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover,
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    color: var(--project-link);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .hero-note {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--p-color);
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .link-prefix {
    color: var(--project-link-prefix);
  }

  .features {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  }

  .feature {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .feature img {
    display: block;
    height: 160px;
    object-fit: contain;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .example {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
    grid-template-columns: 5fr 5fr;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .example-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .example img {
    display: block;
    height: auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  pre {
    background-color: var(--project-card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--project-card-border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
    overflow-x: auto;
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  code {
    font-family: inherit;
  }

  .muted {
    color: var(--p-color);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* Learn */
  .learn {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .learn img {
    display: block;
    height: auto;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    width: 100%;
  }

  /* Modal */
  dialog {
    background-color: var(--project-card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--project-card-border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--body-fg);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    max-width: 860px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    width: 90vw;
  }

  dialog::backdrop {
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
  }

  .modal-header {
    align-items: flex-start;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .modal-title {
    color: var(--p-color);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .modal-close {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: var(--project-link);
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    padding: 0;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .modal-close:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .modal-body img {
    display: block;
    height: auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  /* Footer */
  .page-footer {
    display: flex;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono Variable', 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1199px) {
    .page-body {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    main {
      border-left: none;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--sidebar-border);
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 779px) {
    .features {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .example {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  const modal = document.getElementById('modal-quicksort') as HTMLDialogElement;
  document.getElementById('btn-quicksort')!.addEventListener('click', () => modal.showModal());
  document.getElementById('btn-close-modal')!.addEventListener('click', () => modal.close());
  modal.addEventListener('click', (e) => { if (e.target === modal) modal.close(); });
</script>
